## Project Description

This license applies to the **Tic Tac Toe Web Game**, a front-end web application developed using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. The project is intended for educational, academic, and demonstration purposes and can be executed in any modern web browser using a code editor such as **Visual Studio Code (VS Code)**.

